text: Louis Patrick James Partridge (born 3 June 2003) is an English actor. He began his career as a child actor. His first movie role was in Pan (2015). He had a small role in Paddington 2 (2017). He is known for his role as Viscount Tewkesbury in the Netflix mystery movie Enola Holmes (2020) and its 2022 sequel.
